HOW TO PREPARE 

Mash the ginger, mint and green chilli(Put small pieces of chilli)
Mash it coarsly but finely
Take 2 tbsp of curd in a blending jeera
Add 1/2 tsp jeera powder
Add 1/4 tsp black salt
Add 1/4 tsp salt or as per your taste
Add  chilled water as per your glass quantity
Blend 

SERVE CHILL!